secure_utils.c, spc_open, spc_close and spc_fork are based entirely on
the examples in the 'Secure Programming Cookbook for C++', sections 1.6
and 1.7.

    Secure Programming Cookbook for C and C++
    by John Viega; Matt Messier
    Published by O'Reilly Media, Inc., 2003
    ISBN: 9780596003944

    Examples: https://resources.oreilly.com/examples/9780596003944.git

